{"tid":957341,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"講下 強逼症 討論下 講出黎舒服啲","createTime":"2018-12-27T03:11:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-13T08:43:38.000Z","uid":48065,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"a21cd4effccfe0cdd729751657f2b737b2730e33","tid":957341,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:11:16.000Z","msg":"兩年前患有焦慮症 慢慢變左潔癖 <br />\n而潔癖明顯係強逼症黎既<br />\n<br />\n我會經常洗手 用酒精紙<br />\n認為一啲唔小心既細節 會帶黎莫大既影響 （例如性病 皮膚病 甚至hiv) <br />\n<br />\n個腦會分左邊度係乾淨 邊度係唔乾淨 <br />\n如果掂左唔乾淨既野 可以不停咁掂 直到洗手之後<br />\n<br />\n如果掂左唔乾淨既野 唔記得洗手 再掂乾淨既物件/環境等等 <br />\n<br />\n個腦會認定左 受到污染 變左唔乾淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n要用酒精紙清潔好 <br />\n一日復一日 變到個人好無精神好攰<br />\n<br />\n我有睇過醫生 食過藥 經濟上負擔唔到 所以停左 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有自己上網睇書 睇森田療法之類<br />\n有時會舒緩到果種壓力 但過一排又黎料 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有無人都係咁 一齊傾下 未必有幫助 至少講出黎 可能舒服啲"},{"pid":"9b04e1dd39681825489811d3426896870e8bbfa1","tid":957341,"uid":20847,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:14:35.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098a76d2645a6b48f09a09ba8f7accd129f3a3d0","tid":957341,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"afa6aee8ad1178ed2271e1bb2e683cfffc983193","tid":957341,"uid":48065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"098a76d2645a6b48f09a09ba8f7accd129f3a3d0","tid":957341,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:17:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T03:19:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  想知道點解決到<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"88e1ab8b9d48a9d1141fa04b4653ca69bb6ee93a","tid":957341,"uid":176063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-27T